  "source_code": "#include <stdio.h>\n\nlong long gcd(long long a, long long b) {\n\treturn b == 0 ? a : gcd(b, a % b);\n}\n\nint main() {\n\tlong long n, m, k;\n\n\tscanf(\"%lld%lld\", &n, &k);\n\tm = 1;\n\twhile (k-- > 0)\n\t\tm *= 10;\n\tprintf(\"%lld\\n\", n * m / gcd(n, m));\n\treturn 0;\n}\n",
